{"tid":563142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大懵警維園年宵當值 遺失委任證","createTime":"2018-02-16T15:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T15:57:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"012c1b919430433ad4857f270b65ead7d256e306","tid":563142,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180216/large/1518788743_8299.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180216%2Flarge%2F1518788743_8299.jpg&h=f104e6e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名隸屬柴灣分區的警員今日凌晨於銅鑼灣維多利亞公園當值期間遺失其警察委任證，案件列作「遺失政府財物」處理。警方呼籲市民如拾獲該警察委任證，應立即致電999或把委任證交到就近的警署，案件由柴灣分區跟進調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180216/57842459\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180216%2F57842459&d=O1CNgcZBuqpbfBX1NHLk1o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=16530b76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180216%2F57842459&h=0f7547c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180216/57842459</a>"},{"pid":"b641b13796f0d32a013ea054a57bc6c131306773","tid":563142,"uid":159775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:31:06.000Z","msg":"ho bor ching, gged<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1173d4e9c869b98c30970ee3350831b3236330ac","tid":563142,"uid":162424,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:31:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cc6eec53e715c64b4f4e9eab834e2d6d0195947","tid":563142,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:32:22.000Z","msg":"香港警察呢就黑暗醜惡嘅！"},{"pid":"1bc0f31a94cfcd4226a8557f1cd97a09895346bb","tid":563142,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislik